## CI/CD (`.github/workflows/`)

- Jobs run in parallel where independent (`backend-lint`, `backend-test`, `frontend-lint`, `frontend-test`).
- Cache pip via `actions/cache` keyed on `uv.lock` hash; npm via `actions/setup-node`'s built-in cache.
- Coverage uploaded to Codecov on `backend-test` and `frontend-test`.
- `main` push triggers `build-images` → push to GHCR with tags `latest` and `sha-<short>` → `deploy-fly`.
- PR open/update triggers `preview-deploy` (creates `chat-engine-pr-<num>` Fly app); PR close destroys it.
- Pipeline must complete in **<5 minutes** typical. If a job grows past 3 min, profile and split.

## Forbidden

- Editing `infra/postgres/init.sql` after the initial bootstrap merged — use Alembic.
- Hardcoded image tags or secrets.
- Long-running containers in CI without `timeout-minutes:`.
- Skipping health checks "temporarily".
